The,Cloud,Elements,Marketing,Hub,API,provides,a,single,point,of,access,for,leading,cloud,based,integrated,marketing,services,such,as,Act,On,Eloqua,HubSpot,MailChimp,Mailjet,Marketo,Pardot,Salesforce,Marketing,Cloud,Allbound,SharpSpring,Autopilot,and,Infusionsoft,This,allows,developers,to,manage,their,campaigns,and,contacts,across,multiple,services,using,uniform,API,calls